    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Жисмоний нуқсони, касаллиги ёки саводсизлиги туфайли шартномани имзолай олмайдиган шахснинг номидан расмийлаштирилган кўчмас мол-мулк ҳадя шартномасининг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Тасдиқлов ёзуви ёзилган сана <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> куни ушбу шартномани мен - Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Нотариал идора жойлашган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да жойлашган хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> тарафларнинг хоҳиш-иродасига ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси қонун ҳужжатларига асосан тасдиқладим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шартнома тарафлар томонидан менинг ҳузуримда ўқиб, имзоланди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Жисмоний нуқсони сабабли шартномани ўзи имзолай олмайдиган тарафнинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Шартномани имзолаш имконияти бўлмаган сабаби кўрсатилади</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> туфайли унинг шахсий илтимосига кўра шартномага </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Шартномани имзоловчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Шартномани имзоловчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Шартномани имзоловчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Шартномани имзоловчига паспорт берган ҳудуд </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Шартномани имзоловчига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган) нотариус ҳузурида имзо қўйди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Тарафларнинг ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Жисмоний нуқсони сабабли шартномани ўзи имзолай олмайдиган тарафнинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг ўрнига имзо қўйган </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Шартномани имзоловчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг шахси аниқланди, тарафларнинг муомалага лаёқатлилиги текширилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шахсий мулоқот давомида тарафларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизлигига шубҳа туғилмади ва ушбу нотариал ҳаракатни амалга ошириш даврида нотариал идорада уларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизликлари ҳақида ҳеч қандай маълумотлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 504-моддасига асосан ушбу шартнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Давлат рўйхатидан ўтказилган туман (шаҳар) Кадастр бўлими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Иқтисодиёт ва молия вазирлиги ҳузуридаги Кадастр агентлиги</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да давлат рўйхатидан ўтказилиши лозим.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Шартноманинг реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Давлат божи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Ундириладиган давлат божи миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=